00:12:00,408 --> 00:12:02,196
sometimes I&amp;#39;m also ...

247
00:12:04,1 --> 00:12:05,633
shall we say,

248
00:12:05,657 --> 00:12:09,077
&amp;quot;myopic&amp;quot; when it comesto other people&amp;#39;s feelings,

249
00:12:09,667 --> 00:12:14,945
and that sometimes makes yousay things that hurt other people.

250
00:12:14,969 --> 00:12:18,7370000000001
And I&amp;#39;m not proud of that.

251
00:12:18,761 --> 00:12:19,875
(Applause)

252
00:12:19,899 --> 00:12:21,697
But, at the same time, it&amp;#39;s --

253
00:12:22,978 --> 00:12:26,054
I get people who tell methat I should be nice.

254
00:12:26,796 --> 00:12:32,464
And then when I try to explain to themthat maybe you&amp;#39;re nice,

255
00:12:32,488 --> 00:12:34,7420000000001
maybe you should be more aggressive,

256
00:12:34,766 --> 00:12:38,308
they see that as me being not nice.

257
00:12:38,332 --> 00:12:40,442
(Laughter)

258
00:12:40,466 --> 00:12:42,634
What I&amp;#39;m trying to sayis we are different.

259
00:12:42,658 --> 00:12:44,468
I&amp;#39;m not a people person;

260
00:12:44,492 --> 00:12:46,598
it&amp;#39;s not somethingI&amp;#39;m particularly proud of,

