00:13:10,578 --> 00:13:13,624
it&amp;#39;s just that you&amp;#39;re interestedin really different things.

270
00:13:13,648 --> 00:13:16,551
And coming back to the pointwhere I said earlier

271
00:13:16,575 --> 00:13:20,868
that I was afraid of commercial peopletaking advantage of your work,

272
00:13:20,892 --> 00:13:23,4910000000001
it turned out, and veryquickly turned out,

